snippet.title: ‡§ï‡§ø‡§∏‡§∏‡•á ‡§õ‡§ø‡§™ ‡§∞‡§π‡•á ‡§π‡•à Dr.Haathi? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Due to the availability of fake colours in the market, committee members chose not to celebrate Holi, which has left all of the Gokuldham society's members deeply upset and depressed. How come everyone chose to play Holi all of a sudden? What's the deal? Watch this incredibly fantastic Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Holi special episode to find out.


Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 1364
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Hall Ticket | Episode 3 - Result ka Din | Mini Series | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In this nail-biting episode of "Hall Ticket," anticipation reaches a fever pitch as Ujjwal and his friends eagerly await the moment of truth ‚Äì the unveiling of their board exam results! üìúüò¨
Join Ujjwal and his spirited crew as they navigate the final stretch of their academic journey, brimming with nerves, excitement, and a hint of trepidation. With each passing moment, the tension mounts as they count down the seconds until the fateful announcement.

Discover the world of 'Hall Ticket,' a series capturing the ups and downs while preparing for board exams. Join us as we follow students through late-night study sessions and last-minute reviews, sharing their nerves and excitement.

snippet.title: Every Indian On Holi | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
Happy Holi ap sbko
This Holi Video has every Holi situation we experience. How we Indians celebrate holi . The crazy masti of Holi . Revenge wali holi , pyaar wali holi , dosto ke sath , holi fest ki holi , deciding holi songs playlist , board exams wali holi , holi during school exam , ipl wali holi , grooving on ap dhillon songs , enjoying bhang thandai , beer , gol gappe , dahi bhalle , gujia sweets , getting gifts from relatives gulal , rang , all the colors , pichkari , desi ghee gujia , hugging enemies sorting out the grudges , hitting with water balloons , water guns , dancing , enjoying holika dhayan , the festival of colors , Taking out revenge by applying colours, the foodies, getting painted first by the bf/gf, mixing pakka color into herbal colors, balloon horror created in society that we go through in holi days, and The Best Holi Fight between two groups.. Well you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 

This video is filled with  memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive those fun moments
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour  .. Comment down your Fav Part ,

Punjab se mangaye alloy wheel 
Gaadi set lag ri chori legi feel
Haryane ka chora mein 
Tora pure chetar mein 
That's why girl's wanna 
Give me apna dil 

Raula mach go aage chore gom ke 
Ghar ke bole no hai kom ke 
Panja dabe tyre ghise fir 
Starring ki ye naad tod de 
Han ek jumme ghal gi 
Gadi ke chumma kargi
Gadi ke wheel uche 
Gadi aage halki padgi

Re fame te leke game 
Dono ki naad ghot ke 
Dhar raakhi 
Kadi kariye na mutbhed
Lagre lathi me re ghugru bhi
Ye chan chan baje sottal pe 
Fir bole bairi chachu ji 
Mera ek nisano chuke bhi toh 
Khade gel me bhai chattis 

Jevan ho ya gadi ho
Kadi piche mud ke dekhe no
Yho balakpan me kitne soote
Aajtalak ve dikhe no
Thi garmi khun me pardada ke 
Tabhi Madak bhai jhilti no 
Mero rude hai behaviour 
Toh mujhse katti karle no

Punjab se mangaye alloy wheel 
Gadi set lag ri chori legi feel
Haryane ka chora mein 
Tora pure chetar mein 
That's why girl's wanna 
Give me apna dil 

Tere seher ke me badge gurjar
Leke baddi car 
Rim chondha mare kedo 
Sabki aakhe fat ke char 
Khabbi khali padi
Chaiye lambi thadi naar
Jo pehre no jeans 
Bas pehre suit salwar 
Mahari 2 kila me banri kothi 
Duniyo bhar ki murra jhoti 
Asla ghoda less cash mein
kom saare mauj aari chokhi 
Tyre gadi te bahar 
Peti kar ri bhar bhar bhar bhar
Mittar region NCR 
PCR ghume daily daily 

Goda gadi lathi sari cheejan ne 
chamka ke rakhu

Race lagave gadi te

"Choli Ke Peeche" is a High-Energy Song from the movie "Crew," featuring Tabu, Kareena Kapoor Khan, and Kriti Sanon. Sung by Diljit Dosanjh, Alka Yagnik, Ila Arun, and IP Singh, Music Recreated by Akshay & IP & Lyrics Penned By IP Singh

Lyrics:
Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶ 
Jogiya Ve Mainu Aitthon Door Lae Ja Tu 
Seene Vich Dil Kare Dum Gutkoon 
Mundraan Pua(Pavaa) Ke Naale Majjhiyaan Chara Ke 
Mundraan Pua Ke Naale Majjhiyaan Chara Ke 
Keeta Jeenaan Mushkil Tu Mera 

Choli Ke Peeche Kya Hai 
Chunari Ke Niche Kya Hai 

Dass Mainu Gall Kudiye Tu Kitthon Aayi Ajj 
Jo Bhi Hai Choli Ke Peeche Mujhape Tu De Kharach 
Dekhoon Chhup Chhup Ke Main Tujhey Bolun Sach Sach 
Machne Lagi Tu Baby Too Much Too Much! 
Dekhiyo Na Gir Jaaye Dil Hai Meri 
Judna Ni Phir Haaye Dil Hai Mera 
Dekhiyo Na Gir Jaaye 
Dil Hai Meri Judna Ni Phir Haaye 
Dil Hai Mera Ye Dil Tu De De Apne Yaar Ko, Pyaar Ko.. 

Ku Ku Ku .. 
Resham Ka Lehenga Mera 
Resham Ka Lehenga 
Lehenga Hai Mehenga Mera 
Lehenga Hai Mehenga 
Lehenga Utha Ke Chaloon 
Ghoonghat Gira Ke Chaloon 
Kya Kya Bachaa Ke Chaloon
Raam Ji‚Ä¶ Raam Ji‚Ä¶
Oye Chori.. 

De Bata Tu Kya Hai Tere Seene Vich Na Mila Hai Tere Sa Zamaane Vich. 
Le Mujhey Tu Apni Hi Ore Khichh Naina De Khazaane Tere Lutt Ke Main Hona Rich

snippet.title: Moscow attack: video captures gunmen storming concert hall and shooting dozens dead | BBC News
snippet.description:
*** WARNING graphic content

Russia‚Äôs state security services say at least forty people are dead, and over a hundred injured, after heavily armed gunmen burst into a packed theatre near Moscow, ¬†and opened fire.

It happened at the Crocus Concert Hall, part of which is in flames, after explosives were detonated. 

Video images show the gunmen, in military camouflage, walking through the venue and shooting their victims.

Ukraine has said it had nothing to do with the atrocity. 

The Islamic State group has said that it was behind the attack but that has not been confirmed. 

Clive Myrie presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Steve Rosenberg in Moscow, Sarah Smith in Washington, Sarah Rainsford in Kyiv and security correspondent Gordon Corera. 

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

For more news, analysis and features visit: www.bbc.com/news 

#BBCNews

snippet.description:
The prawn recipe is one of the tastiest recipe ever. Today we cook prawns with butter and garlic. First we tawa fry the shrimp then we add it to with butter and garlic. We use coriander leaves instead of parsley the reason is it is not available in our village.

The taste is spicy!

snippet.title: Monkey Man | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
They took everything from him. He will get his revenge. 
#MonkeyManMovie Only in Theaters April 5

---

Oscar¬Æ nominee Dev Patel (Lion, Slumdog Millionaire) achieves an astonishing, tour-de-force feature directing debut with an action thriller about one man‚Äôs quest for vengeance against the corrupt leaders who murdered his mother and continue to systemically victimize the poor and powerless.

Inspired by the legend of Hanuman, an icon embodying strength and courage, Monkey Man stars Patel as Kid, an anonymous young man who ekes out a meager living in an underground fight club where, night after night, wearing a gorilla mask, he is beaten bloody by more popular fighters for cash.

After years of suppressed rage, Kid discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the city‚Äôs sinister elite. As his childhood trauma boils over, his mysteriously scarred hands unleash an explosive campaign of retribution to settle the score with the men who took everything from him.

Packed with thrilling and spectacular fight and chase scenes, Monkey Man is directed by Dev Patel from his original story and his screenplay with Paul Angunawela and John Collee (Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World).

The film‚Äôs international cast includes Sharlto Copley (District 9), Sobhita Dhulipala (Made in Heaven), Pitobash (Million Dollar Arm), Vipin Sharma (Hotel Mumbai), Ashwini Kalsekar (Ek Tha Hero), Adithi Kalkunte (Hotel Mumbai), Sikandar Kher (Aarya) and Makarand Deshpande (RRR).

Monkey Man is produced by Dev Patel, Jomon Thomas (Hotel Mumbai, The Man Who Knew Infinity), Oscar¬Æ winner Jordan Peele (Nope, Get Out), Win Rosenfeld (Candyman, Hunters series), Ian Cooper (Nope, Us), Basil Iwanyk (John Wick franchise, Sicario films), Erica Lee (John Wick franchise, Silent Night), Christine Haebler (Shut In, Bones of Crows) and Anjay Nagpal (executive producer of Bombshell, Greyhound). 
 
Serving as executive producers are Jonathan Fuhrman, Natalya Pavchinskya, Aaron L. Gilbert, Andria Spring, Alison-Jane Roney and Steven Thibault.
 
Universal Pictures presents a Bron Studios production, a Thunder Road film, a Monkeypaw production, a Minor Realm/S‚ÄôYa Concept production, in association with WME Independent and Creative Wealth Media.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Alien: Romulus | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The sci-fi/horror-thriller takes the phenomenally successful ‚ÄúAlien‚Äù franchise back to its roots: While scavenging the deep ends of a derelict space station, a group of young space colonizers come face to face with the most terrifying life form in the universe. The film stars Cailee Spaeny (‚ÄúPriscilla‚Äù), David Jonsson (‚ÄúAgatha Christie‚Äôs Murder is Easy‚Äù), Archie Renaux (‚ÄúShadow and Bone‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù), Spike Fearn (‚ÄúAftersun‚Äù), Aileen Wu. Fede Alvarez (‚ÄúEvil Dead,‚Äù ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt Breathe‚Äù) directs from a screenplay he wrote with frequent collaborator Rodo Sayagues (‚ÄúDon‚Äôt Breathe 2‚Äù) based on characters created by Dan O‚ÄôBannon and Ronald Shusett. ‚ÄúAlien: Romulus‚Äù is produced by Ridley Scott (‚ÄúNapoleon‚Äù), who directed the original ‚ÄúAlien‚Äù and produced and directed the series‚Äô entries ‚ÄúPrometheus‚Äù and ‚ÄúAlien: Covenant,‚Äù Michael Pruss (‚ÄúBoston Strangler‚Äù), and Walter Hill (‚ÄúAlien‚Äù), with Fede Alvarez, Elizabeth Cantillon (‚ÄúCharlie‚Äôs Angels‚Äù), Brent O‚ÄôConnor (‚ÄúBullet Train‚Äù), and Tom Moran (‚ÄúUnstoppable‚Äù) serving as executive producers.

snippet.title: üî¥BIG BREAKING: MS DHONI QUITS AS CSK CAPTAIN, RUTURAJ TO LEAD CHENNAI
snippet.description:
MS Dhoni has stepped down as captain of the Chennai Super Kings, handing over the captaincy to young opener Ruturaj Gaikwad ahead of the IPL 2024.

"MS Dhoni has handed over Chennai Super Kings' captaincy to Ruturaj Gaikwad ahead of the start of TATA IPL 2024. Ruturaj has been an integral part of Chennai Super Kings since 2019 and has played 52 matches in IPL during this period. The team looks forward to the upcoming season," CSK issued a statement on captaincy change.

--------------------------------------------------------

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: TVF's Very Parivarik | Official Trailer | Weekly Show | Releasing On 22nd March
snippet.description:
Get ready as we flip the script of the "perfect family" stories because, in our world, it's not all about loving your family!

Presenting you the trailer of TVF's First Weekly Show - Very Parivarik with episodes as long as your lunch breaks. Gather your family (or not, we won't judge!)  for a dose of entertainment you never knew you needed because the chaos is about to begin with TVF and IKEA present Very Parivarik brought together by Urban Company.

@ikeaindia  is a global leader in life at home. Creating a better everyday life with 7500+ products for every space, style, and budget. Shop furniture, decor, storage and organisation solutions, and more. 
Visit the IKEA store, https://www.ikea.in/parivarik or download the IKEA app.

Urban Company is Asia‚Äôs most trusted home & personal services app. Choose from a range of top-rated & trained professionals, from appliance technicians to massage therapists: https://www.urbancompany.com
 
A TVF Weekly Show

Created by: Vaibhav Bundhoo, Arunabh Kumar
Directed by: Vaibhav Bundhoo
Produced by: Arunabh Kumar
Writing: Vaibhav Bundhoo, Dishant Verma, Anand Kumar, Deeksha Choudhary, Harshpal Singh, Swarnadeep Biswas, Sidharth Sodhi
Executive Producers: Vijay Koshy, Vaibhav Bundhoo

Cast: Srishti Rindhani, Pranay Pachauri, Paritosh Sand, Kanupriya Shankar Pandit, Luv Vispute, Arun Kumar, Badri Chavan, Vidhushi Koul, Prerna Thakur, Khusbhu Baid 

#TVF #VeryParivarik #Family

snippet.title: The Fall Guy | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
He‚Äôs only the stuntman, but he‚Äôs stealing the show.
#TheFallGuyMovie Only in Theaters May 3. 

------

He‚Äôs a stuntman, and like everyone in the stunt community, he gets blown up, shot, crashed, thrown through windows and dropped from the highest of heights, all for our entertainment. And now, fresh off an almost career-ending accident, this working-class hero has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job. What could possibly go right? 

From real life stunt man and director David Leitch, the blockbuster director of Bullet Train, Deadpool 2, Atomic Blonde and Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw and the producer of John Wick, Nobody and Violent Night, comes his most personal film yet. A new hilarious, hard-driving, all-star apex-action thriller and love letter to action movies and the hard-working and under-appreciated crew of people who make them: The Fall Guy. 

Oscar¬Æ nominee Ryan Gosling (Barbie, La La Land, Drive) stars as Colt Seavers, a battle-scarred stuntman who, having left the business a year earlier to focus on both his physical and mental health, is drafted back into service when the star of a mega-budget studio movie‚Äîbeing directed by his ex, Jody Moreno, played by Golden Globe winner Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place films, Sicario)‚Äîgoes missing.

While the film‚Äôs ruthless producer (Emmy winner Hannah Waddingham; Ted Lasso), maneuvers to keep the disappearance of star Tom Ryder (Golden Globe winner Aaron Taylor-Johnson; Bullet Train) a secret from the studio and the media, Colt performs the film‚Äôs most outrageous stunts while trying (with limited success) to charm his way back into Jody‚Äôs good graces. But as the mystery around the missing star deepens, Colt will find himself ensnared in a sinister, criminal plot that will push him to the edge of a fall more dangerous than any stunt.

Inspired by the hit 1980s TV series, The Fall Guy also stars Winston Duke (Black Panther franchise) and Academy Award¬Æ nominee Stephanie Hsu (Everything Everywhere All at Once). 

From a screenplay by Hobbs & Shaw screenwriter Drew Pearce, The Fall Guy is produced by Kelly McCormick (Bullet Train, Nobody, Atomic Blonde) and David Leitch for their company 87North, and by Ryan Gosling and by Guymon Casady (Game of Thrones, Steve Jobs and executive producer of the upcoming series Ripley) for Entertainment 360. The film is executive produced by Drew Pearce, Entertainment 360‚Äôs Geoff Shaevitz and the creator of the original Fall Guy television series, Glen A. Larson.

Website: http://www.TheFallGuyMovie.com
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/thefallguymovie 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/thefallguymovie 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@Universalpics 
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/@UniversalPictures
X: https://twitter.com/thefallguymovie

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
